<p>
Counsel for Alliance for Community Media, who will be arguing 
before the Supreme Court on behalf of all petitioners:
<p>
Michael Greenberger <br>
Shea & Gardner, Washington, D.C.
<p>	
TO OBTAIN A SAMPLE TAPE OF FREE SPEECH TV PROGRAMMING, CONTACT:<br>
Dani Newsum, Free Speech TV, 303-442-5693, or Emily Whitfield, 
ACLU, 212-944-9800, x426.
</p>

</blockquote>
