HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 14:18:01 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 17:39:46 GMT
Content-length: 3098
Content-type: text/html
