<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><IMG SRC="/graphics/worker.gif"></P>
<H1>Campaign for Fairness in the Workplace
</H1>
<P></P>
<DL>
<DT><FONT SIZE="+2">ACLU Marks Labor Day With Workplace Rights Video and
Report, Launches Campaign for Fairness in the Workplace</FONT></DT>
<DD><A HREF="/news/n090196a.html">Press Release: September 1, 1996</A>Redoubling
its efforts to protect the rights of employees in the workplace, the American
Civil Liberties Union today launched its &quot;Campaign for Fairness in the
Workplace&quot; with the release of a 12-minute video and a white paper report
that documents how employees are being increasingly spied upon and monitored at
work.</DD></DL>
<P></P>
<DL>
<DT><FONT SIZE="+2">Report Update: A State of Emergency in the Workplace</FONT></DT>
<DD><A HREF="/library/wrrpt96.html">1996 White Paper: Surveillance,
Incorporated</A></DD></DL>
<P></P>
