<DOCOLDNO>IA083-000585-B031-232</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.aclu.org:80/library/pbr1.html 204.243.96.55 19970213125801 text/html 8012
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 12:56:48 GMT
Last-modified: Saturday, 27-Jan-96 17:52:25 GMT
