<DOCOLDNO>IA082-000569-B046-94</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.aclu.org:80/court/11th.html 204.243.96.55 19970213120857 text/html 16234
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
