<P ALIGN="CENTER">No. 95-1441</P>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><B>In the<BR>Supreme Court of the United States</B></P>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">October Term, 1996</P>
<HR WIDTH="70%">
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><B>LINDA J. BLESSING</B>, <I>Petitioner</I>,</P>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">v.</P>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><B>CATHY FREESTONE</B>, <I>et al</I>., <I>Respondents</I>.</P>
<HR WIDTH="70%">
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P ALIGN="CENTER">On Writ of <I>Certiorari</I> to the United States Court of
Appeals for the Ninth Circuit</P>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><B>Brief <I>Amicus Curiae</I> of the American Civil
Liberties Union and the Arizona Civil Liberties Union in Support of Respondents</B></P></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE></BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P ALIGN="CENTER"><B>TABLE OF CONTENTS</B></P>
