<P><B>I. THE COURT SHOULD REJECT PETITIONER'S INVITATION TO REVERSE OR SHARPLY
LIMIT THE HOLDING OF <I>MAINE v. THIBOUTOT</I></B></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<P><B>A. <I>Maine v. Thiboutot</I> Was Correctly Decided</B></P>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
