<P>Annis v. County of Westchester,<BR>36 F.3d 251 (2d Cir. 1994) . . . . . . .
. . . . . . . . . . . . . . 24</P>
<P>Baker v. Delo,<BR>38 F.3d 1024 (8th Cir. 1994) . . . . . . . . . . . . . .
