<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT12-B26-110</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA083-000585-B036-115</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.aclu.org:80/court/cohen.html 204.243.96.55 19970213131117 text/html 19864
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 13:10:01 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 05-Feb-96 21:54:08 GMT
