http://www.aclu.org:80/library/pbp6.html 204.243.96.55 19970213135403 text/html 13959
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 13-Feb-97 13:52:46 GMT
