<head>
<title>ACLU in the Courts</title>
<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<blockquote>
<img src="/graphics/courthdr.gif">
<center>
<p><b>  No. 95-124<br>

     In The
     SUPREME COURT OF THE UNITED STATES
     October Term, 1995
                                                
<P>
Denver Area Educational Telecommunications Consortium, Inc. and American Civil Liberties
Union,
Petitioners,<p>
v.
<P>
 Federal Communications Commission
and United States of America, et al.,
Respondents.                                                                 
<P>

</b></center>
<br>
<img src="../graphics/rbline.gif" width=100%><br>
On Writ of Certiorari To The United States
Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit
<p>
BRIEF FOR PETITIONERS<br>
New York, New York<br>
December 27, 1995
<p>
TABLE OF CONTENTS
<blockquote>
     <a href="#qp">QUESTIONS PRESENTED</a><br>  
    <a href="#list"> LIST OF PARTIES</a><br>
<a href="#ta">TABLE OF AUTHORITIES</a><br>      
